task.summary: Initial Check-in for my local repositories.
Checkpoint for continued work on BuildandPlay. Significant progress to a working example; now have working resources that are compatible with melon example.

Moved several providers to ORMLite. Had to leave Chunk provider as-is due to lack of support for complex Primary Keys. Brought in latest version of ORMLite Refactored several data handling sections to their own classes. Starting getting rid of raw SQL calls where possible

Finished up support for H2, now defaults to embedded mode. Can initialize a blank database using the provided SQL and import a map with nothing else present. Added support for bringing in maps with tilesets that aren't present in the database.

Cleaned up some of the providers. Cleaned up the realmInfo jsp by using providers directly out of the Spring scope (instead of inline SQL >.<) Refactored some of the javascript objects, particularly for realms and images. Added some missing providers to the application context. Fixed up how the importer works under certaiin situations. Added a msising field to the tilesetData class
